{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/umbraco-community/awesome-umbraco/readme","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c199de9b-8363-5a1c-8fe0-8a74c6cf6a58","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-umbraco-awesome-umbracov9\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-umbraco-awesome-umbracov9\" aria-label=\"awesome umbraco awesome umbracov9 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Umbraco! <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/main/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a> <a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/download/releases/900\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Umbraco-v9-blue\" alt=\"UmbracoV9\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A collection of awesome <a href=\"https://github.com/umbraco/Umbraco-CMS/\">Umbraco CMS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/umbraco/Umbraco-CMS/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.7k</span></span></a> packages, resources and shiny things.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Inspired by <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\">awesome lists</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">222.8k</span></span></a>. For general C#/.NET please see the <a href=\"https://github.com/quozd/awesome-dotnet/\">awesome-dotnet</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/quozd/awesome-dotnet/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">15.5k</span></span></a> collection!</p>\n<h3 id=\"contributing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contributing\" aria-label=\"contributing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contributing</h3>\n<p><strong>Contributions are always welcome!</strong></p>\n<p>Please read the <a href=\"https://github.com/umbraco-community/awesome-umbraco/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">contribution guidelines and quality standard</a> page before making a pull-request. If you see a resource or package here that is no longer maintained, please submit a pull request to help improve this collection.</p>\n<p>Thank you to all <a href=\"https://github.com/umbraco-community/awesome-umbraco/graphs/contributors\">contributors</a>, you are awesome and this list wouldn't be possible without you! The goal is to build a categorized community-driven collection of very well-known resources.</p>\n<h3 id=\"versions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#versions\" aria-label=\"versions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Versions</h3>\n<p>This list is for Umbraco v10 packages. However, we also have lists for older versions! Check them out too.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/umbraco-community/awesome-umbraco/blob/master/UMBRACO-V9.md\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Umbraco-v9-blue\" alt=\"UmbracoV9\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/umbraco-community/awesome-umbraco/blob/master/UMBRACO-V8.md\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Umbraco-v8-blue\" alt=\"UmbracoV8\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/umbraco-community/awesome-umbraco/blob/master/UMBRACO-V7.md\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Umbraco-v7-blue\" alt=\"UmbracoV7\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#official\">Official</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#backoffice-extensions\">Backoffice extensions</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#form-builders\">Form Builders</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#property-editors\">Property Editors</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#developer-tools\">Developer tools</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#deployment\">Deployment</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#ecommerce--crm\">eCommerce &#x26; CRM</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#starter-kits\">Starter Kits</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#code-libraries\">Code Libraries</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please note * indicates that the package is commercial or may require a license to unlock all features.</p>\n<h2 id=\"official\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#official\" aria-label=\"official permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Official</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://umbraco.com\">Umbraco website</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://codegarden20.com/\">CodeGarden Conference</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/documentation/\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/download/\">Download</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/forum/\">Forum</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pro/umbraco\">Meetups</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/umbracohq\">Official YouTube Channel</a> - tutorials and other helpful videos about Umbraco products.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community\" aria-label=\"community permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://h5yr.com/\">#h5yr</a> - High Five, You Rock!</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://24days.in/umbraco-cms/\">24 Days In Umbraco</a> - yearly advent calendar for Umbraco content.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/community/blog-posts/\">Blog Posts</a> - blog posts by members of the Umbraco community and Umbraco HQ.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://candidcontributions.com/\">Candid Contributions</a> - a fortnightly podcast discussing all things Umbraco and open source.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://skrift.io/\">Skrift</a> - a monthly magazine for sharing knowledge in the Umbraco community.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/umbracoffee\">umbraCoffee</a> - a weekly YouTube series discussing recent Umbraco news.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/umbracocommunity/\">Official YouTube Channel</a> - the Umbraco community YouTube channel.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"backoffice-extensions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#backoffice-extensions\" aria-label=\"backoffice extensions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Backoffice extensions</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/plumber-workflow-for-umbraco/\">Plumber</a> - adds a heap of useful bits and pieces to Umbraco, to allow multi-staged workflow approval.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/translation-manager/\">Translation Manager*</a> - lets you handle all of the steps of the translation process from within Umbraco.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/hot-chilli-page-not-found-manager\">Page Not Found Manager</a> - Manage your sites 404 page(s) from Umbraco.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/contentment/\">Contentment</a> - A handy collection of Umbraco components developed for use in your Umbraco projects.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/website-utilities/skybrud-redirects/\">Skybrud.Umbraco.Redirects</a> - Redirects manager for Umbraco.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/simpleredirects/\">SimpleRedirects</a> - Redirects manager for Umbraco.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/newsletter-studio-the-email-studio/\">Newsletter Studio*</a> - Responsive email editor to create emails for all clients.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/backoffice-themes/\">Backoffice Themes</a> - Allows choosing your own themes for in the backoffice.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"form-builders\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#form-builders\" aria-label=\"form builders permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Form Builders</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://umbraco.com/products/umbraco-forms/\">Umbraco Forms*</a> - A package to easily add customisable forms to your website. <strong>(Developed by Umbraco HQ)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"property-editors\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#property-editors\" aria-label=\"property editors permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Property Editors</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/website-utilities/meganav/\">Meganav</a> - A flexible, draggable link picker for constructing site navigation menus, big or small.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/ueditornotes/\">uEditorNotes</a> - Provides a way to display instructional messages for content editors, at the point of content entry.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"seo-tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#seo-tools\" aria-label=\"seo tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SEO Tools</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://soetemansoftware.nl/seo-checker\">SEO Checker*</a> - find common SEO issues in your Umbraco website.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/seotoolkit/\">SeoToolkit</a> - Package that provides SEO features like meta fields, redirects, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"developer-tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#developer-tools\" aria-label=\"developer tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Developer tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://soetemansoftware.nl/cmsimport\">CMSImport*</a> - import content or members from any datasource into Umbraco.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/developer-tools/usync/\">uSync</a> - Syncing tool for reading and writing the database elements to disk.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/developer-tools/diplo-god-mode/\">Diplo God Mode</a> - Exposes a lot of information for developers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/developer-tools/datefolders/\">DateFolders</a> - Creates Datefolders (year/month(/day)) for the specified doctype for Umbraco</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/developer-tools/alphabetfolders/\">AlphabetFolders</a> - Creates AlphabetFolders for the specified doctype for Umbraco</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.com/packages/backoffice-extensions/konstrukt/\">Konstrukt*</a> - Backoffice UI builder through code.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"deployment\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deployment\" aria-label=\"deployment permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Deployment</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/umbraco/Umbraco.Deploy.Contrib\">Deploy Contrib</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/umbraco/Umbraco.Deploy.Contrib\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 